headline.main: Progres of the Whitewashing Process--Aaron Barr.

docs.lead_paragraph: To the Editor of the Express: SIR: It is with pleasure that I comply with your request. Some time during the year preceding the death of Col. BURR, when on my way to visit him in company with my kinsman, tile late OGDEN E. EDWARDS, we were told that it was reported there were among his papers letters from reputable females which compromised their characters.

docs.lead_paragraph: Details of the Mexican news, brought to NewOrleans by the Tennessee, are important and exciting. When the mail left Vera Cruz there had been several days' fighting in the Capital between President COMONFORT and the Constitutional Party on the one hand, and the Pronunciados, including the Conservadores, Santanistas and the Church on the other.
